{"id":212232,"date":[{"year":1951,"month":1,"day":21}],"page":"5","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"社会大学","column":"读者接待室,医药顾问","genre":"","count":"205","ytitle":"","mtitle":"干性皮脂溢出症疗法","ftitle":"","authors":["邵钧"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"答白洁之先生:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你所述症状，很像干性皮脂溢出症，是一种皮肤病，故发屑奇多，并不是细胞新生代谢快速所致，这病可致落发，它的疗法:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1、保持发部清洁(经常洗涤，若为男性，则可将头发剃去)。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"2、涂擦下药R.Sulfurprecip10."},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Resorctional3.0"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Taleum6.o"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Spiritviniad30.0S.用牙刷或小毛刷刷入发部。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"3、少吃食脂肪之食物"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(邵钧医师答)"}]}